oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hank Snow Studio Recordings - 1980-12-19
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recordings are of a variety of studio recordings of Hank Snow (musician) and Kelly Foxton (musician). The accompanying band is unidentified. The recordings were engineered by Bill Vandevort and produced by RCA Records. The recordings are compiled December 19, 1980.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Snow; Kelly Foxton
